targets.query: SELECT mean("value") FROM "ipmi_sensor" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$node$/ AND ("name" = 'system_fan_1a' OR "name" = 'system_fan_2a' OR "name" = 'system_fan_3a' OR "name" = 'system_fan_4a' OR "name" = 'system_fan_5a' OR "name" = 'system_fan_6a')) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("value") FROM "ipmi_sensor" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$node$/ AND ( "name" = 'pw_consumption' OR "name" = 'ps1_input_power' OR "name" = 'ps2_input_power')) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "ipmi_sensor" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$node$/ AND "name" = 'cpu1_temp' ) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
